Class DatabaseStreamStorage

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.StreamStorage
      • net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.DatabaseStreamStorage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @Entity
 @Configurable
 @I18NFile(symbolPrefix="net.proteusframework.data.filesystem.DatabaseStreamStorage",
          i18n=@I18N(symbol="ERROR DELETE NO DATA",l10n=@L10N(value="No data to delete")))
public class DatabaseStreamStorage
extends StreamStorage
    Implements stream storage using the DataSourceStreamManager which stores streams as chunks in a single table.

    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com)

        public String getLocationSummary(FileEntity file)
        Description copied from class: StreamStorage
        Get the location summary for the stream. This method is intended for diagnostic purposes, such as error reporting. The intended audience is developers and system administrators. Enough information must be provided such that the data may be found quickly and precisely. Examples include "Database in table stream, record 53", "/mnt/share/path/file-5112.jpg", etc.
